parameters:
Clea: Mr. Goat...! Please wait, I will lift the curse right
now!

Goat from the Bulk Gang: Ugh, agh! G-get away, hurry,
I-I'm...!

Clea: Please don't give up! I have brought a priest as
instructed by the shrine maiden!

Priest Sophia: Yes... If I'm with Eleo-chan, we should be
able to do something.

Sister Eleo: Please endure just a little longer! I will
definitely free you from your suffering!
Priest Sophia: Eleo-chan, are you okay!?

Priest Sophia: This... part of his body is already... Clea-
chan, Mr. Goat has already turned into an ogre...

Clea: Let's fight... but! It's to heal you, to keep you
alive!

Clea: Huff... huff... I won't let you lay a finger on
him...!
Thief Nora: Y-Yes, that's right! We will protect Mr. Goat!

Mage Relm: As a mage, I have a mission to fundamentally lift
curses, I swear on the honor of mages!

Priest Sophia: Eleo-chan, what should we do? What should we
do!?

Sister Eleo: Please calm down. After stopping the bleeding,
I will perform the recovery. Please follow my lead.

Sister Eleo: Goddess Imiserinos, grant a warm embrace to the
wounded.

Priest Sophia: Goddess Imiserinos, bestow a warm embrace
upon the wounded.

Sister Eleo: Please focus! Please treat Mr. Goat with the
same intensity as me!

Priest Sophia (I have never thought of myself as a priest,
so it is not easy to simply claim the position of a priest.)

Priest Sophia (But they taught me that the desire to save
someone is not related to one's position or status...)
Priest Sophia: So please, I beg of you...

Priest Sophia: Please survive and persevere! By saving
yourself, there are people who will be saved as well!

Thief Nora: The scent of the monster has disappeared!
Sophia-san and the others have restored everything!

Mage Relm: The blood disappeared along with the dark
magic... There is a high possibility that blood is related
to the curse.

Priest Sophia: Haa... haa... Is this... really okay? Is it
truly okay!?
Priest Sophia: Eleo-chan, are you really okay...?

Sister Eleo: It's alright now. You succeeded because you
truly wanted to save people.
Sister Eleo: Priest Sophia, your dedication is admirable.
Sister Eleo: As a priest, I am proud to be your mentor.
Priest Sophia: Sister Eleo... Thank you very much.
Sister Eleo: You did your best, Sophia-san!

One-armed Opro: If my prey is only monsters and there are
[humans] there, there is no point in continuing.
Clea: Sigh... It didn't feel like I was alive.

Clea: Let's ask the Bulk Corps to take care of Goats-san's
care.
Clea: Let's go report to the priestess.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea (Incredibly strong... Truly a monster... No, that's not
it)
Clea: It shouldn't be like this! Goats-san, please wake up!

Clea: The warriors of the Bulk Corps shouldn't be defeated
by curses!
Goats, the one who resists curses, ....
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
One-armed Opro: I didn't make it in time...

One-armed Opro: For the sake of our old friend... and for
the sake of our new friend, I offer your head to the goddess
Actina.

One-armed Opro: Without pride or friends, die as a lone
monster.

One-armed Opro: I'm sorry... New friend, I'm sorry... Old
friend... Another victim has been claimed.
One-armed Opro: I've broken another promise...

Would you like to retry the battle? If you choose No, it
will result in a game over.

The leader of the Bulk Gang, Goat, says, We will now perform
the rite of passage to become warriors.

Goat, the leader of the Bulk Gang, says, I want you to
discern the true nature of the curse.

Goat of the Bulk Gang says, First, we swear to continue
fighting as members of the Bulk Gang at the great tree where
our ancestors rest.

Goat of the Bulk Gang says, Next, we swear to continue
fighting for our comrades.

Goat of the Bulk Gang says, The oath to our comrades is to
rub our thumbs together, where our blood flows.

Sister Eleo: There is no mistake! That action is the
movement that creates the [curse]!
Bulk Gang's senior warrior: ...Based on what?

Mage Relm: There are cases where incantations are not
necessary for magic. This time, it should be triggered by
the location, blood, and movement.

Mage Relm: There should be separate conditions for becoming
an ogre, but I don't know what those conditions are...

Bulk Gang's senior warrior: You bastards...! Are you mocking
our ritual and traditions?!

Bulk Gang's senior warrior: Just a bunch of imperial people!
You deceive us, followers of Imiserinos!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: If the part where blood flows
disappears, there won't be any problem, right?

Sister Eleo: At that time, the blood disappeared along with
the curse. The parts that were not involved with the blood
are still intact, so it's safe.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: We will follow your advice and change
a part of the ritual starting today.

Bulk Gang's senior warrior: This is a ritual that our
ancestors have protected! What will happen to the pride of
the Bulk Gang?!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Even if it means becoming an ogre, we
will protect our homeland... This is magic born from such a
wish, I suppose.

Bulk Gang's Goat: However, it has become a curse, something
unnecessary for us now.

Bulk Gang's Goat: There should be things that we should
inherit from our ancestors and things that we consider
unnecessary and should disappear.

Bulk Gang's Goat: No matter how the times may change, the
warriors of the Bulk Gang will always be the strongest!

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Hahaha, don't make that face! It is
us who will uphold the tradition of being the strongest!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: 'On behalf of the brave warriors
of the Bulk Brigade, I would like to express our gratitude.'

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: This is something that is only
given to true warriors. I hope you will use it during your
arduous adventure.

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: If you ever find yourself in
trouble, please rely on us. Especially in battlefields that
require the strongest warriors, we would be grateful!

One-armed Opro: It seems like everything has been resolved,
huh?

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: I've only recognized the goddess
Actina, but the goddess Imiserinos isn't too bad either!

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: I must go and express my gratitude
to the shrine maiden.

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: ...If you and I were to fight, who
do you think would win?
One-armed Opro: Without a doubt, it would be me.

One-armed Opro: That's a different story if you were an
ogre. As a human like you... I can't say for sure what the
outcome would be.

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: Hahaha, mighty warriors! I look
forward to meeting you on the battlefield someday!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 誇り高き血族

Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'If there's ever a chance, I would
like to have a match with you all as warriors!'
